.DT
query_stop_responding
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_stop_responding

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_stop_responding -  This method returns the flag determining the toggling of the responses of the npc.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_stop_responding()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 to the npc will not respond, 0 it is responding
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/response_mon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the flag determining the toggling of the
responses of the npc.
If this is set to 1, then the npc will stop responding to
messages.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_stop_responding()

.EP

